{"tid":1020012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"莎莎：新春旺丁不旺財 期內同店銷售大跌8%","createTime":"2019-02-13T10:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T10:50:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"908f2daa07f5b1e8f23bc1365a209b213a08b60d","tid":1020012,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190213/s00010/fc8da49ca131d0e050f0593a849b9ab0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190213%2Fs00010%2Ffc8da49ca131d0e050f0593a849b9ab0.jpg&h=920669ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n莎莎國際（0178）公布2019年農曆新年期間（2月5日至11日）的銷售數據，港澳零售銷售按年跌4.8%，同店銷售跌幅更大，達7.9%，香港市場零售銷售按年跌5%。<br />\n<br />\n莎莎指出，內地客消費加倍審慎，就算香港入境處的數據顯示，農曆新年期間，內地訪港遊客大增31.6%，但「旺丁不旺財」，集團整體交易量下跌2.8%，內地客交易量更要跌3.4%，本地客交易量就跌1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n集團解釋，銷售表現遜預期，除了中美貿易戰，股市及樓市持續波動影 響消費意欲，去年同期的基數亦較高所致。集團續稱，會加強推廣活動，例如與支付平台推出優惠，以刺激銷售。另外，集團會減除低生產力的產品，降低庫存成本及提高營運效益，再引入高銷量的產品，改善產品組合。<br />\n<br />\n莎莎今日收報3.08元，微跌0.3%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1550047961412&amp;issue=20190213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1550047961412%26issue%3D20190213&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=ac95a983\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1550047961412%26issue%3D20190213&h=29669aab\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1550047961412&amp;issue=20190213</a>"},{"pid":"713fde1541fe95344acff7d0be43dd5b3fc33d13","tid":1020012,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"正常，老尖班自由行好多兩手空空咁死返去膠鐵站"},{"pid":"68d63057ef6395f7cc92c4d1d03a017df9a073f4","tid":1020012,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T10:50:19.000Z","msg":"香港越來越來又低消費又寒酸既支那人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}